cscie97.asn1.knowledge.engine

Class Triple

  • java.lang.Object
    • cscie97.asn1.knowledge.engine.Triple

  • public class Triple
extends java.lang.Object
    The Triple class represents a unique Triple (Subject, Predicate, Object) within the KnowledgeGraph. A Triple contains references to Nodes ( subject and object ) and Predicate.
    Author:
    Siddharth Singh

    • Constructor Detail

      • Triple

        public Triple(Node subject,
      Predicate predicate,
      Node object)
        Triple constructor. Keeps reference of nodes and predicates. Nodes and predicates are created only for new identifiers so that number of node and predicate instances are minimized ( flyweight pattern ).
        Parameters:
        subject - node corresponding to subject
        predicate - node corresponding to predicate
        object - node corresponding to object
